      <body>Hello,

I am marking this as invalid as using [:destryo] with the brackets is correct.  Looking at the Rails API documentation I show the following on this page http://api.rubyonrails.org/classes/ActionController/Resources.html:

map.resources :posts, :only =&gt; [:index, :show] do |post|
  post.resources :comments, :except =&gt; [:update, :destroy]
end

Mike Riley</body>
